# Discord Support TOS

Before asking for support read this:

### Introduction

we are the support team and ask you to follow the TOS to keep our high support strands\
The `#ia-community-help` gets over 40+ help requests per day.\
Most of the requests (76% ) **** can be solved by reading the wiki, take your time to read it.

### Getting Support

The support team is helping only verified members, you must verify your account in \
