#### Adding Friends

If you are working as a team **one verified account** must be present in the chat.

### General rules

{% hint style="success" %}
The Support team is a group of volatiles, they are not getting paid.\
The support team helps me keep up, and helps you solve problems
{% endhint %}

#### Respect

They are trying to help you, don't be a jerk... problems can take time to fix.\
DON'T DO THINGS THAT ARE NOT NICE.  (We don't need to tell you what's good & bad)

#### Tag

Don't spam tag support members, and do not tag me!

#### Languages

the support team is built from people all around the world, you can ask for support in the following languages:\
